data.title: Manuscripts of book reviews by Robert Bontine Cunninghame Graham., 1932-1935.
data.text: Includes: (i) Review of 'Don Segundo Sombra', by Ricardo Guiraldes, translated by Harriet de Orni≈° (London, 1935). (ii) Review of 'Bronco Charlie', by G T Erskine (London, 1935). (iii) Review of 'East again', by Walter B Harris (London, 1933). (iv) Review of 'The black tents of Arabia', by C R Raswan (London, 1935). (v) Review of 'Enchanted sand', by D J Hall (London, 1932).
